      "para_id": "Q005315.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(o 1) For Nanše , the mighty lady , the lady of the boundaries , his lady , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , made an eternal thing appear : he restored Niĝin , her beloved city , built the E-sirara , the mountain rising from among the houses , and built his beloved divine audience chamber from fragrant cedarwood inside it ."
    }
  ],
